<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:CivilizationAmigaAGA.png" class="image" title="Civilization popularized the detailed empire management that has become a staple of 4X strategy games."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a7/CivilizationAmigaAGA.png/180px-CivilizationAmigaAGA.png" width="180" height="113" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
